:

1. *Njima* sam rekao da ću doći. (I told them I would come.)
2. Nisu znali šta da *njima* kažu. (They didn't know what to say to them.)
3. Ona je uradila sve *njima*. (She did it all for them.)
4. *Njima* je potrebna pomoć. (They need help.)
5. Njegove misli su bile u potpunosti posvećene *njima*. (His thoughts were completely devoted to them.)